AKMS Polish Underfolder in 7.62x39, imported by Century International Arms.

*Hogue overmolded rubber stock set with 4 optional picatinny rails;
*5 TAPCO magazines (31-round capacity);
*Polish drop case;
*Polish sling;
*Polish cleaning kit
*TAPCO G2 Trigger;
*TAPCO slotted muzzle brake;
*Green mountain barrel;
*Front sight adjustment tool;
*Broken shell extractor;
*$100 worth of Hornady 123-grain SST.

Gun runs flawlessly with every type of ammo and shoots nice, tight groups. Easy to stow away in truck compartments or other small spaces. $800, firm, cash only, no trades. Located in downtown Dallas.
